{{vgname|星际公民|en=Star Citizen}}是未來將在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]和[[Linux|Linux]]公开的{{link-en|太空飛行模擬遊戲|Space flight simulation game|太空模擬}}電子遊戲。<ref name="arstechnica_2014-08-03">{{cite web |url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2014/08/star-citizen-and-the-triumphant-record-smashing-return-of-chris-roberts/ |title=Star Citizen and the triumphant, record-smashing return of Chris Roberts |last=Hutchinson |first=Lee |date=2014-08-03 |website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] |publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]] |oclc=52157687 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140807225307/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2014/08/star-citizen-and-the-triumphant-record-smashing-return-of-chris-roberts/ |archive-date=2014-08-07 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-10-19 }}</ref>《星际公民》由四个主要要素组成：第一人称太空作战、开采、探索和贸易。星际公民为一个大型多人第一人称射击游戏，并且有定制的{{link-en|私人服务器|Private server}}，<ref name="Tringham">{{cite book |last1=Tringham |first1=Neal Roger |date=2014 |title=Science Fiction Video Games |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=0o5qBAAAQBAJ |deadurl=no |location=Boca Raton |publisher=Taylor & Francis |pages=413–415 |isbn=9781482203882 |oclc=868642041 |accessdate=2014-11-10 |via=Google Books |archive-date=2017-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107190939/https://books.google.com/books?id=0o5qBAAAQBAJ }}</ref><ref name="TheMittani_2012-10-19">{{cite interview |subjectlink=Chris Roberts (game developer) |interviewer=Marc Scaurus |title=Exclusive Interview: Star Citizen's Chris Roberts |url=http://themittani.com/features/exclusive-interview-star-citizens-chris-roberts |date=2012-10-19 |accessdate=2014-10-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021232822/http://themittani.com/features/exclusive-interview-star-citizens-chris-roberts |archivedate=2012年10月21日 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>也有名为《''Squadron 42''》的单人模式和名为《''Star Citizen''》的多人模式。<ref name="arstechnica_2014-08-03" />游戏是建立于改良的[[CryENGINE|CryEngine]]并将由支援所有主要VR頭戴裝置<ref name="Williams">{{cite book |last1=Williams |first1=Kevin |date=2014 |title=Out-of-Home Immersive Entertainment Frontier |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=1h6rBAAAQBAJ |deadurl=no |location=Farnham |publisher=Ashgate Publishing |pages=86–87 |isbn=9781472426956 |via=Google Books |access-date=2015-12-18 |archive-date=2017-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107124923/https://books.google.com/books?id=1h6rBAAAQBAJ }}</ref>。

《星際公民》及《''Squadron 42''》皆設定在30世紀[[銀河系|銀河系]]中心虛構的地球聯合帝國（United Empire of Earth，UEE），一個晚期[[羅馬帝國|羅馬帝國]]的類似體制。遊戲主題是在UEE上的[[公民|公民]]，透過玩家的行動而謀生，例如完成一段時期的兵役。這會預期到公民將會享受某些在遊戲中的福利，例如支付低稅率，但準確的詳細資料仍然有待確定。

遊戲的一個明顯焦點放在玩家的互動上，玩家行為會有影響力，也會受[[虛擬經濟|動態經濟系統]]所影響。

《星際公民》及《''Squadron 42''》由{{link-en|克里斯·羅伯茲|Chris Roberts (game developer)}}的公司{{link-en|Cloud Imperium Games|Cloud Imperium Games}}、{{link-en|IllFonic|IllFonic}}和歐洲的Foundry 42製作。市場銷售則由Cloud Imperium Games[[子公司|子公司]]Roberts Space Industries負責。

== 遊戲開發 ==
=== 公開募資 ===
星際公民截至2016年底透過[[群眾募資|群眾募資]]獲得了超過一億四千萬美金的資金，是目前第二高資金的群眾募資活動（僅次於The DAO，一個建立在[[電子貨幣|電子貨幣]]以太幣合約機制上的投資基金），也是有史以來募資到最多資金的遊戲。

2012年十月，星際公民的開發團隊使用了[[WordPress|WordPress]]的群眾募資插件IgnitionDeck在官方網站上開放了[[群眾募資|群眾募資]]活動<ref>{{cite web|last=Christenson|first=Shawn|title=Crowdfunding a Video Game|url=http://ignitiondeck.com/id/crowdfunding-a-video-game/|publisher=IgnitionDeck|accessdate=2016-12-31|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129102650/https://ignitiondeck.com/id/crowdfunding-a-video-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNBCCrowdfunding">{{cite web |url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/102021804 |title=The man who made $50 million ditching Kickstarter |last=Morris |first=Chris |date=2014-09-24 |publisher=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |type=Report |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140924032114/http://www.cnbc.com/id/102021804 |archive-date=2014-09-24 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2016-12-31 }}</ref>，過了約一個禮拜後也在大型群眾募資網站[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]上進行募資活動<ref name="Auto6N-7">{{Kickstarter|cig/star-citizen|Star Citizen}}</ref>，原本Kickstarter目標的五十萬美金迅速地被超過，原本的募資期限延長了十天來募取更多的資金<ref name="PCGamer_2012-10-28">{{cite web |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/star-citizen-rsi-campaign-extended-new-stretch-goals-announced/ |title=Star Citizen: RSI campaign extended, new stretch goals |last=Sykes |first=Tom |date=2012-10-28 |website=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |publisher=Future US |type=News |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019101518/http://www.pcgamer.com/star-citizen-rsi-campaign-extended-new-stretch-goals-announced/ |archive-date=2014-10-19 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2016-12-31}}</ref>，在募資活動結束前兩天星際公民以四百二十萬美金創下有史以來群眾募資最多資金的遊戲的紀錄<ref name="Auto6N-9">{{cite web |url=https://robertsspaceindustries.com/comm-link/transmission/12792-Unlock-Hades-System |title=Stretch goals update |date=2012-11-17 |accessdate=2016-12-31 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112035622/https://www.robertsspaceindustries.com/comm-link/transmission/12792-Unlock-Hades-System |dead-url=no }}</ref>，當募資活動結束時總資金已達到六百二十萬美金。<ref name="CNBCCrowdfunding"/>

在Kickstarter活動結束後，開發團隊繼續在官方網站上進行募資<ref name="CNBCCrowdfunding"/>，到了2013年中旬，星際公民以不到一年的短時間共募得了一千五百萬美金成為當時金額最高的群眾募資活動。<ref name="Jacobs Sparks">{{cite book |date=2014 |editor1-last=Jacobs Sparks |editor1-first=Karen |editor2-last=Shepherd |editor2-first=Melinda C. |editor3-last=Bauer |editor3-first=Patricia |editor4-last=Duignang |editor4-first=Brian |editor5-last=Gregersen |editor5-first=Erik |display-editors=1 |title=Britannica book of the year: 2014 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LccRAwAAQBAJ |deadurl=no |location=Chicago |publisher=[[Encyclopaedia_Britannica|Encyclopaedia Britannica]] |page=213 |isbn=9781625131225 |oclc=892531428 |accessdate=2016-12-31 |via=Google Books |archive-date=2019-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190522141051/https://books.google.com/books?id=LccRAwAAQBAJ }}</ref>2014年[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]以$39,680,576美金的紀錄承認星際公民創下了“透過群眾募資所獲得的最高單一款項”的紀錄。<ref name="GuinessWorldRecord">{{cite book |chapter=Crowdsourcing |chapterurl=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/2015/preview/files/assets/basic-html/page16.html |editor1-last=Glanday |editor1-first=Craig |editor2-last=Fall |editor2-first=Stephen |editor3-last=Mackey |editor3-first=Roxanne |editor4-last=Bebbington |editor4-first=Theresa |editor5-last=Lorimer |editor5-first=Marie |display-editors=1 |title=Guinness World Records 2015 |url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/2015/preview/files/assets/basic-html/page17.html |deadurl=no |location=London |publisher=[[Guinness_World_Records|Guinness World Records Limited]] |publication-date=2014 |page=141 |isbn=978-1-90-884363-0 |oclc=869770714 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006065530/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/2015/preview/files/assets/basic-html/page17.html |archivedate=2014-10-06 |accessdate=2016-12-31 }}</ref>在2014年8月15日所舉行的[[Gamescom|Gamescom]]活動上，克里斯·羅伯茲宣布群眾募資活動已正式超過了五千萬美金<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2014/08/18/star-citizens-crowdfunding-total-shoots-past-50-million/ | title=Star Citizen's crowdfunding total shoots past $50 million | date=2014-08-18 | publisher=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | accessdate=2016-12-31 | archive-date=2014-08-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140825220913/http://www.pcgamer.com/2014/08/18/star-citizens-crowdfunding-total-shoots-past-50-million/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，在2016年12月官方網站所顯示的總募款金額超過了一億四千萬美金。<ref name="RSI_StretchGoals">{{cite web |url=https://robertsspaceindustries.com/funding-goals |title=The Stretch Goals |website=Roberts Space Industries |access-date=2016-12-31 |archive-date=2018-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719155246/https://robertsspaceindustries.com/funding-goals |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

